nodes.text: The Duinuogwuin were a group who, during the time of the High Republic Era, were galactic neighbors of the expanding Galactic Republic. Chancellor Lina Soh hoped that her Great Works, including the Starlight Beacon space station, but particularly the showcase of what the Republic had to offer at the Republic Fair on the planet Valo, would allow for the government to build bridges with nearby groups such as the Duinuogwuin.
